%% ====================================================================
%% Sequence 04: Task Edit (owner check + authorization error)
%% Task Management System v1.2
%% ====================================================================
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as ユーザー
  participant Browser as ブラウザ
  participant Sec as Spring Security
  participant Filter as TenantContextFilter
  participant Ctrl as TaskController
  participant UC as UpdateTaskUseCase
  participant AuthZ as TaskAuthorizationDomainService
  participant TaskRepo as TaskRepositoryImpl
  participant Audit as AuditLogger
  participant DB as MySQL

  User->>Browser: 編集ボタン押下 → フィールド変更 → 保存
  Browser->>Sec: PUT /api/tasks/101
  Sec->>Filter: 認証OK (userId=2, role=MEMBER)
  Filter->>Ctrl: forward (TenantContext set)
  Ctrl->>Ctrl: @Valid TaskUpdateRequest
  Ctrl->>UC: execute(UpdateTaskCommand)

  UC->>TaskRepo: findById(taskId=101, tenantId=11)
  TaskRepo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE id=101 AND tenant_id=11
  DB-->>TaskRepo: task (owner_id=1)
  TaskRepo-->>UC: Task

  UC->>AuthZ: canBeEditedBy(task, userId=2, role=MEMBER)
  Note over AuthZ: 編集権限の詳細ルールは TaskAuthorizationDomainService が SSOT<br/>(基本設計書 §6.2.1 参照)

  alt 認可失敗 (所有者ではない、ADR-0005 で Tenant Admin 特権は撤廃済)
    AuthZ-->>UC: throw TaskOwnershipException
    UC->>Audit: log(UPDATE_TASK_DENIED, actor, taskId=101)
    Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs (action='UPDATE_TASK_DENIED')
    UC-->>Ctrl: TaskOwnershipException
    Ctrl-->>Browser: 403 E_FORBIDDEN<br/>"タスクの編集は所有者のみ可能です"
    Browser-->>User: エラー表示
  else 認可成功 (userId=ownerId のケースのみ)
    AuthZ-->>UC: ✓
    UC->>UC: task.rename(newTitle)<br/>task.reschedule(newDueDate)<br/>task.changePriority(newPriority)<br/>... (Domain メソッドで不変条件チェック)
    UC->>TaskRepo: save(task)
    TaskRepo->>DB: UPDATE tasks SET title=..., due_date=..., updated_at=NOW()<br/>WHERE id=101 AND tenant_id=11
    DB-->>TaskRepo: 1 row affected
    UC->>Audit: log(UPDATE_TASK, actor, taskId=101, diff={title:[old,new], ...})
    Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs
    UC-->>Ctrl: Task
    Ctrl-->>Browser: 200 OK + 更新後 Task JSON
    Browser-->>User: 一覧/詳細を再描画
  end

  Note over AuthZ,Audit: 認可違反は audit_logs に必ず記録<br/>(NIST AC-3: アクセス制御の監査)
